        <main class='mui-column -s12 -m9'>
            <div class='mui-content-container'>



                <div class='_separate-3'>
                    <h2 class='_bigger-2' id='overview'>Overview</h2>

                    <p class='mui-p _separate-1'>Muilessium is the UI framework or rather a collection of UI components and helpers for developing responsive and accessible websites. This framework written in LESS and ES6 and can be included in a project as is or can be easily customized for your needs. Muilessium supports WAI-ARIA attributes and generates most of them automatically.</p>

                    <div class='mui-row _separate-1'>
                        <div class='mui-column -s6 -m4 template-preview'>
                            <img class='mui-image _lazy-load' data-src='/images/landing-template-1-preview.png'>
                            <a href='/landing-template.html'>Landing template example</a>
                        </div>
                        <div class='mui-column -s6 -m4 template-preview'>
                            <img class='mui-image _lazy-load' data-src='/images/blog-template-1-preview.png'>
                            <a href='/blog-template.html'>Blog template example</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>



                <div class='_separate-5'>
                    <h3 class='_bigger-2' id='grid-overview'>Grid</h3>

                    <p class='mui-p _separate-1'>Muilessium uses a classic grid with 12 columns based on floats. Rows and columns have classes .mui-row and .mui-column and columns can have options -s* for a small screen, -m* for a medium screen and -l* for a large screen. Default breakpoints are 400, 600 and 1200px.</p>

                    <div class='grid-preview _separate-2'>
                        <div class='mui-row'>
                            <div class='mui-column -s1 -grey-4-bg -white _text-center _line-2r _smaller-1'>-s1</div>
                            <div class='mui-column -s11 -grey-4-bg -white _text-center _line-2r _smaller-1'>-s11</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class='mui-row'>
                            <div class='mui-column -s3 -grey-4-bg -white _text-center _line-2r _smaller-1'>-s3</div>
                            <div class='mui-column -s9 -grey-4-bg -white _text-center _line-2r _smaller-1'>-s9</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class='mui-row'>
                            <div class='mui-column -s6 -m4 -l6 -grey-4-bg -white _text-center _line-2r _smaller-1'>-s6 -m4 -l6</div>
                            <div class='mui-column -s6 -m8 -l6 -grey-4-bg -white _text-center _line-2r _smaller-1'>-s6 -m8 -l6</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class='mui-row'>
                            <div class='mui-column -m6 -l2 -grey-4-bg -white _text-center _line-2r _smaller-1'>-m6 -l2</div>
                            <div class='mui-column -m6 -l10 -grey-4-bg -white _text-center _line-2r _smaller-1'>-m6 -l10</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class='code-example _separate-2 _smaller-2'>
                        <pre class='prettyprint lang-html'>
    &lt;div class='mui-row'&gt;
        &lt;div class='mui-column -s1'&gt;-s1&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class='mui-column -s11'&gt;-s11&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class='mui-row'&gt;
        &lt;div class='mui-column -s3'&gt;-s3&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class='mui-column -s9'&gt;-s9&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class='mui-row'&gt;
        &lt;div class='mui-column -s6 -m4 -l6'&gt;-s6 -m4 -l6&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class='mui-column -s6 -m8 -l6'&gt;-s6 -m8 -l6&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class='mui-row'&gt;
        &lt;div class='mui-column -m6 -l2'&gt;-m6 -l2&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class='mui-column -m6 -l10'&gt;-m6 -l10&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;</pre>
                    </div>
                </div>



                <div class='_separate-5'>
                    <h3 class='_bigger-2' id='page-layout-overview'>Page layout</h3>

                    <p class='mui-p _separate-1'>Basic page layout includes header, page container and footer. This layout is the simplest way to create a sticky footer, but IE11 does not support flexbox greatly, so we have some incorrect behavior in it.</p>

                    <div class='code-example _separate-2 _smaller-2'>
                        <pre class='prettyprint lang-html'>
    &lt;header class='mui-page-header'&gt;header&lt;/header&gt;
    &lt;div class='mui-page-container'&gt;...&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;footer class='mui-page-footer'&gt;footer&lt;/footer&gt;</pre>
                    </div>
                </div>



                <div class='_separate-5'>
                    <h3 class='_bigger-2' id='helpers-overview'>Helpers</h3>

                    <p class='mui-p _separate-1'>Muilessium has a number of helpers, no need to add description for every of them - just look at src/less/helpers.less.</p>
                </div>



